dmenu compatibility can be achieved using these arguments:
.TP
\f[CR]\-S\f[R]
Don\[cq]t sort matches
.TP
\f[CR]\-i\f[R]
Use case\-insensitive matching
.TP
\f[CR]\-nb color\f[R]
Set the normal background color
